stories

1. as user i want to search for recipies, so i can find new ideas for meals
2. as user, i want to be able to update the number of servings, so that i can cook a meal for diffrent number of people
3. as a user, i want to bookmark recipes, so that i can review them later
4. as a surer i want to be able to create my own recipeis, so that i have them all organized in the same app
5. as a user i want to see my bookmarks and own recipes when i leave the app and come back later

feature

1. search , pagination for result , display detail for recipe
2. change servings
3. bookmark
4. upload own recipies, user create recipy will be auto marked, user can see only their own recipe
5. bookmark data in localstorage, on page load read bookmarks from page
